Gomillion's ground game halts Baldwin skid against Cardinals 
Sat, Oct 24, 2015 @ 12:19 am 
The Times-Union 
BALDWIN 20 
BISHOP SNYDER 7 
Maurice Gomillion rushed for 154 yards and a touchdown, helping the Indians snap their losing skid at Bishop Snyder (2-6). ... Reynaldo Grey caught a 21-yard scoring pass from Kolby Wilcox for Baldwin (3-5). ... The Indiansâ€™ defense held the Cardinals to 91 total yards.
